### Create a new article (author only)
POST http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type:application/json

{
    "author":"69896d574cb43c1ef358c4d9",
    "title":"java",
    "category":"prog",
    "content":"java.util.*"
}

### Get all articles by a specific author
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69896d574cb43c1ef358c4d9

### Update an article by ID (author only)
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/698990b93afe0b8cce8eccd5
Content-Type:application/json

{
    "author":"69896d574cb43c1ef358c4d9",
    "title":"python",
    "category":"prog",
    "content":"functions,numpy,pandas"
}

### Delete a specific article by a specific author
DELETE  http://localhost:4000/author-api/users/69896d574cb43c1ef358c4d9/articles/6989a52a512c981d34f9813b

